-Expected in 2016. Together with the Parliament, UNDP is planning to conduct series of consultations with the representatives of local governance authorities and executive authorities on the local level to discuss the recommendations for improvement of the system of local governance proposed during the diagnostic review;

-UNDP engaged international expert with vast experience in parliamentary work to share the experience in constitutional review and best practices in developing quality legislation. During the 2-day roundtable more than 120 parliamentarians and parliament staff learned modern techniques and methodologies of developing quality legislation corresponding to international standards. UNDP also developed a brochure for parliamentarians containing basic information for the new parliamentarians on developing legislation, etc.;

